Package: git-unas
Version: @VERSION@
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCH@
Maintainer: demiurge28 <@MAINTAINER_EMAIL@>
Depends: libc6, systemd
Homepage: https://github.com/demiurge28/git-unas
Description: Git clone, tar, and encryption admin UI for Ubiquiti UNAS
 A Node.js web admin page served on 127.0.0.1:7892 and exposed
 via nginx at https://<device>/git-unas/. Provides a browser UI
 to run git clone, tar archiving, file encryption, and scheduled
 backups on a Ubiquiti UNAS device running UniFi OS.
